this is a profanity plugin that inserts the song that is now playing on your last.fm into your xmpp status

adjust the source code to your liking (insert your last.fm api key, and replace username)

requirements:
profanity
curl

installation:
make && make install 

(no need for root)

in profanity do
/plugin load profanity-lastfm.so

(only needed once)
